title: AVG FREE EDITION (2012) zorromax
description:
AVG Anti-Virus Free 2012

Pros:

Very good scores in removal and malware blocking tests. High ratings from independent labs. Protection against phishing and exploits. Toolbar with safe search, Facebook access, and more. Fast scan.

Cons:

Rootkit scan is separate from whole computer scan. Phishing and exploit protection less effective than antivirus.
